{
  "texts": [
    "For example, in a study [G1], when AI practitioners were asked, \"Do your AI development practices take into account ethics, and if yes, how?",
    "\", all respondents (N=6) answered \"No\".",
    "This indicates that AI companies lack clear tools and methods that help AI practitioners implement ethics in AI.",
    "Another study [G19] concluded that there is a lack of tools that support continuous assurance of AI ethics.",
    "A participant in a study [G19] stated that it was challenging for them as they had to rely on manual practice to manage ethics principles during AI system development."
  ]
}